  "content": "<p>穿越到坎帕阶早期的蒙古，估计带上嘴就行了，人类在那个时代的蒙古是巨兽。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6526ea2fce699a14fa463c2f735888dc_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"149\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2f9fe22445a7b4c72b9a61f452782c46_hd.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"360\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;360&#39; height=&#39;149&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"149\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2f9fe22445a7b4c72b9a61f452782c46_hd.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"360\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6526ea2fce699a14fa463c2f735888dc_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>菜龙互啄的时代，人类是巨兽</figcaption></figure><p>别看不起原角龙，原角龙在当时几乎没有天敌，日子远比很多时代的巨龙滋润。。。。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-52249e3698f5a2c1118b22f105d545a7_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"429\" data-rawheight=\"292\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-38bbfe74a8589a21c65f89e0abcfe441_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"429\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-52249e3698f5a2c1118b22f105d545a7_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;429&#39; height=&#39;292&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"429\" data-rawheight=\"292\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-38bbfe74a8589a21c65f89e0abcfe441_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"429\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-52249e3698f5a2c1118b22f105d545a7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-52249e3698f5a2c1118b22f105d545a7_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>战斗力不会比鹅低吧？</figcaption></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><fig